Office of the Under Secretary of Defense (OUSD) - $1.9M Budget
Question: How did you perform financial analysis and risk assessment within the $1.9 million budget for mergers and acquisitions?

•	Allocated $500,000 for financial analysis.

•	Allocated $600,000 for risk assessment.

•	Included hiring financial analysts, conducting due diligence, and engaging risk management experts.

•	Prioritized these activities and closely monitored the budget.

•	Used the remaining budget for stakeholder engagement, reporting, and contingency planning.

•	Ensured a balanced approach to managing the program.
